Products.description: The Bill Ripken 1989 Fleer FF Error is one of the most notable error cards of all time. Bills brother Cal had a much better career and Bill is most known for this card. An unidentified jokester wrote “Fuck Face” on Ripkens bat knob before he posed with it for his card photoshoot. This prank went unnoticed by Fleer before being packed off into the 1989 Fleer set. After Fleer caught wind of the mistake, this cards were corrected and new versions were released with boxes covering the obscenity.
